snippet.title: Base Commander Cinematic Opener
snippet.description:
Base Commander is set to be a 5v5 MOBA game that will similar to League of Legends and DOTA 2, but instead of pushing lanes and trying to destroy the enemy nexus, teams fight for control of uniquely powered bases. 

When controlled by a team, these bases grant that entire team a unique bonus like attack damage, speed, or a powerful ability. To learn more about Base Commander, check us out on Steam! 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1900960/Base_Commander/#:~:text=Base%20Commander%20on%20Steam&text=A%205v5%20MOBA%20where%20players,control%20of%20uniquely%20powered%20bases.

Discord: 
https://discord.gg/basecommander
